{"tid":1958954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙大成街街市門口有人賣二手口罩","createTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:45:24.000Z","uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c075e346c7bbdd929d89bfe1700db537f511958","tid":1958954,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"今朝買完餸出嚟<br />\n見到有個阿婆喺門口賣口罩，2蚊1個<br />\n我覺得太平，一定有古怪，所以就行埋去睇<br />\n見到掛耳條帶同口罩邊黃黚黚好核突<br />\n就踢爆佢<br />\n佢話係間廠設計到有少少螢光黃咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話邊有廠會整到一撻撻漬呀<br />\n你唔好再賣啦<br />\n人哋買咗，隨時奶嘢都唔知呀<br />\n<br />\n佢唔聽我勸，繼續賣<br />\n<br />\n我就企咗喺度一陣<br />\n有人嚟睇我就話係二手罩千祈咪買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲時候仲害人害物<br />\n等天收啦死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2LZSXV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2LZSXV.png&h=62bc1d66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78e1f3d45ccbe3de5a90941d477c2723e71a8f15","tid":1958954,"uid":334861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0061f208c0f0ed7a30570f7c2c5edc912c02a746","tid":1958954,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"消毒啦"},{"pid":"ba63e8b12fe5a5a7fca7389535f2e64e964e6b0f","tid":1958954,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78e1f3d45ccbe3de5a90941d477c2723e71a8f15","tid":1958954,"uid":334861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"已經like and share咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass